{"prompt": "Generate a website for a restaurant chain. The website should be sophisticated and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Culinary Haven</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Garamond', serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f8f8f8;\n            color: #333;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #a00000;\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            letter-spacing: 3px;\n        }\n        nav {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n        }\n        nav a {\n            color: #a00000;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: #d00000;\n        }\n        .hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(rgba(160, 0, 0, 0.6), rgba(160, 0, 0, 0.6)), url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x800/a00000/ffffff?text=Elegant+Dining') no-repeat center center/cover;\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 100px 0;\n            min-height: 500px;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            flex-direction: column;\n        }\n        .hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n        .section {\n            padding: 60px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        .section h3 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            color: #a00000;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            border-bottom: 2px solid #a00000;\n            display: inline-block;\n            padding-bottom: 5px;\n        }\n        .menu-item, .gallery-item, .contact-info {\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n        .menu-item h4, .gallery-item h4 {\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            color: #a00000;\n        }\n        .menu-item p, .gallery-item p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            max-width: 600px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n        .gallery {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 20px;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n        .gallery-item img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 250px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            display: block;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n        .contact-info {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            line-height: 1.8;\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #333;\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 1em;\n        }\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .container {\n                width: 90%;\n            }\n            header h1 {\n                font-size: 2.5em;\n            }\n            .hero h2 {\n                font-size: 2.2em;\n            }\n            .hero p {\n                font-size: 1.2em;\n            }\n            .section h3 {\n                font-size: 2em;\n            }\n            nav a {\n                display: block;\n                margin: 10px 0;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n    <link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Garamond:wght@400;700&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Culinary Haven</h1>\n            <nav>\n                <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n                <a href=\"#menu\">Our Menu</a>\n                <a href=\"#gallery\">Gallery</a>\n                <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n            </nav>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section class=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Experience Exquisite Flavors</h2>\n            <p>Discover a world of culinary delights crafted with passion and the finest ingredients. Welcome to Culinary Haven, where every meal is a masterpiece.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\" class=\"section\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h3>Our Story</h3>\n            <p style=\"font-size: 1.2em; line-height: 1.7; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;\">\n                Founded in 2005, Culinary Haven started with a simple vision: to bring sophisticated yet accessible dining experiences to our community. We believe in the power of food to connect people and create lasting memories. Our chefs blend classic techniques with modern innovation, ensuring every dish is a harmonious balance of flavor and presentation.\n            </p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"menu\" class=\"section\" style=\"background-color: #f4f4f4;\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h3>Signature Dishes</h3>\n            <div class=\"menu-item\">\n                <h4>Seared Scallops with Saffron Risotto</h4>\n                <p>Tender, pan-seared scallops served atop creamy saffron-infused risotto, finished with a delicate lemon zest.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"menu-item\">\n                <h4>Wagyu Beef Wellington</h4>\n                <p>Prime Wagyu beef tenderloin, mushroom duxelles, and prosciutto, encased in a golden puff pastry.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"menu-item\">\n                <h4>Truffle Mushroom Pappardelle</h4>\n                <p>Fresh pappardelle pasta tossed in a rich, creamy truffle mushroom sauce, garnished with fresh parsley.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"gallery\" class=\"section\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h3>A Glimpse of Elegance</h3>\n            <div class=\"gallery\">\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/a00000/ffffff?text=Elegant+Interior\" alt=\"Restaurant Interior\">\n                    <h4>Ambiance</h4>\n                    <p>Our dining spaces are designed for comfort and sophistication.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/a00000/ffffff?text=Gourmet+Dish\" alt=\"Gourmet Dish\">\n                    <h4>Culinary Art</h4>\n                    <p>Each dish is a feast for the eyes and the palate.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/a00000/ffffff?text=Wine+Pairing\" alt=\"Wine Pairing\">\n                    <h4>Perfect Pairings</h4>\n                    <p>Complement your meal with our curated selection of fine wines.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\" class=\"section\" style=\"background-color: #f4f4f4;\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h3>Visit Us</h3>\n            <div class=\"contact-info\">\n                <p><strong>Address:</strong> 123 Gourmet Lane, Culinary City, CC 54321</p>\n                <p><strong>Phone:</strong> (123) 456-7890</p>\n                <p><strong>Email:</strong> info@culinaryhaven.com</p>\n                <p><strong>Hours:</strong> Mon-Sat: 5:00 PM - 10:00 PM | Sun: Closed</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Culinary Haven. All Rights Reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        document.querySelectorAll('nav a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}